Ch. 124, TEKS for Marketing Education.
(2)
The student knows the importance of marketing as well as the functions of marketing.
The student is expected to: (A) (B) (C) explain the marketing concept; describe each marketing function and how it relates to the fashion industry; explain how each component of the marketing mix contributes to successful marketing; explain the importance of target markets; describe advantages and disadvantages of market segmentation and mass marketing; and research trends and emerging technologies affecting fashion marketing.
